Package: FederatedAnalysisDataSHIELD
Title: Federated Analysis using DataSHIELD — Reproducibility Package
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("David", "Sarrat González", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "david.sarrat@isglobal.org"),
    person("Michael", "Ochola", role = "aut"))
Description: Reproducibility package for the methods paper "Federated Analysis
    using DataSHIELD". Stands up a fully local three-site federation and runs a
    real federated analysis over OMOP CDM data with DataSHIELD and dsOMOP v2.
    The articles here are executed against that live federation, so the
    rendered output is the genuine result of running the workflow end to end.
